Description:
Generalization of the <ctype.h> ispunct() function and the
<wctype.h> iswpunct() function.

Files:
lib/unictype/ctype_punct.c
lib/unictype/ctype_punct.h
lib/unictype/bitmap.h

Depends-on:
unictype/base

configure.ac:
